<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Although the BP's effect has a mega long cast time.....it takes no mana. Also these effect are similar to Jboots so they can be cast while running without interruption. I agree the effect will be too late to save someones arse but that is what you have spells for. This effect will be great for healing everyone up after a battle.</font></td></tr></table>
